    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a Locator/ID Separation Protocol (LISP) shared message type for defining future extensions and conducting experiments without consuming a LISP Packet Type codepoint for each extension.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document obsoletes RFC 8113.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
